snippet.title: Healing Spree Teaser
snippet.description:
Steam page : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1271110/Healing_Spree/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/HealingSpreeHQ
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/HealingSpree
Website: http://healing-spree.com/ 

Healing Spree is an insane couch co-op game for 1 - 4 players. You and your friends must treat patients and defend against the overwhelming pandemic. Are you ready to dive into the life of a doctor with your friends?
